Installation instructions for Mediawiki-Akismet.

1) Install Mediawiki and verify that it's working.
2) Create the directory INSTALLDIR/extensions/Aksimet on the server and copy the Mediawiki-Aksimet files to the directory.
3) Copy config_example.php to config.php and edit the variables in it to match your server settings.
4) Run the SQL commands in create_table.sql on your MySQL server.
